{"tid":1336843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[快閃活動］狗屋外牆翻新，以及爬蟲藝術館","createTime":"2019-07-21T06:21:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T20:58:02.000Z","uid":63808,"like":54,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f14f8968d040d8867f1ad8780121981925d578b0","tid":1336843,"uid":63808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T06:21:07.000Z","msg":"想提議組小隊去18區狗屋，以及高鐵站做外牆翻新工程，需要噴漆之類，寫大字；做爬蟲藝術館，需要田雞，草蜢，曱甴，紅油漆，單車鎖鎖上大門，每隊約10至20人，為快閃活動，希望大家能幫忙集思廣益<br />\n<br />\n原因，大量狗仔集中灣仔，希望能用小量人力資源，做至分散狗力，令灣仔義士輕鬆d。如果成功，會做成十分大的noise,想像下全港狗屋都比人做外牆翻新，工程巴打記得中英對照，方便推埋比國際媒體。<br />\n<br />\n安全需知，保護好自己身份是常識吧，呢個為一個快閃活動，目的在於制做國際輿論，做完即閃保護自己，如有cctv 大家識做啦，如果有狗仔，可以考慮同佢上油，太多狗太危險就快閃，重點在擾敵，敵駐我擾，不要送頭。優先目標係全部人全身而退，其次先係外牆翻新同爬蟲藝術館的建造。如不幸被補，<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WEkNzz3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWEkNzz3.gif&h=8c52841e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位香港人，加油，希望大家先去遊行，之後先再分隊行動，啱聽就推下post，唔同意可以留言討論下，or負皮，由佢沉。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f0qUY2Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff0qUY2Y.png&h=e2ec84b0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d9rXWPE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd9rXWPE.png&h=7f5568f7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XHmEqHZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXHmEqHZ.png&h=723a5357&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uaOLmgk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuaOLmgk.png&h=9ab51edc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hqivxn1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHqivxn1.png&h=a695f290&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n0a55H1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn0a55H1.png&h=2021f7f9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QWLeeBm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQWLeeBm.